name: Amoebic - Blue Edition
description:
Click/tap to distribute food.

Amoebas will sense food nearby. With enough food, amoebas will produce offspring.

Larger amoebas will have a greater chance of producing mutated offspring. Color mutations are influenced by the parent's characteristics.

When the maximum population of ten amoebas is reached, the oldest will shrink and die.

Refreshing the page will restart the simulation. You will always begin with a blue amoeba.
